title: Storage case

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a storage case, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view of a storage case;
FIG. 2 is a front elevation view of the storage case of FIG. 1;
FIG. 3 is a top plan view of the storage case of FIG. 1;
FIG. 4 is a side elevation view of the storage case of FIG. 1, the opposite side being a mirror image of FIG. 4;
FIG. 5 is a back elevation view of the storage case of FIG. 1; and,
FIG. 6 is a bottom plan view of the storage case of FIG. 1.
The broken lines showing structure in all figures are for illustrative purposes only and form no part of the claimed design.
